I"(<h3 id="1-cyclamen">1. Cyclamen</h3>
<p>If you’re not sure what flowers to give as a present, Cyclamen is a good option. Cyclamen plants in pots make a lovely present for almost everyone on your list. Moms, children, sisters, and even that new love interest will appreciate these flowers. Cyclamen are lovely holiday presents and can even be utilized as hostess gifts. The blooms bloom over several months, adding a dash of color to the cold, gloomy days(Jay, 2020).
<img src="/images/all1.png" alt="" />
<br /></p>

<hr />

<h3 id="2-orchid">2. Orchid</h3>
<p>Potted orchids are also an excellent gifting option, no matter the occasion.</p>

