<h3 id="3-tansy">3. Tansy</h3>
<p>Tansy flowers are excellent gifts for a wide range of events. Flowers can be given as gifts for birthdays, anniversaries, marriages, or simply as a romantic gesture(Gaumond, 2021).</p>

<h4 id="tagcampanulales-asteraceae">Tag:<a href="/campanulales">Campanulales</a>, <a href="/asteraceae">Asteraceae</a></h4>
